    <div class="col-md-12">
        <p> Finally arrived in the room, a side sea view and a side mountain view awaited us. Sometimes nice. We don't have the latest room, but it was very chic - and above all big. After we unpacked everything, we went in search of something edible. On the way there we crossed the hotel complex and found that you can no longer get a single couch at lunchtime. Let's see how it will be the next few days. </p>
        <p> When we arrived at the beach, we completed a short video call at the birthday child at home and then went to the restaurant next to the hotel. Here we shared a really good pizza and one or the other refreshing drink. Then it went briefly into the small supermarket around the corner, the minibar was filled with water, and then Siesta was announced - the inhumane up time was slowly noticeable. </p>
        <p> Later we walked along the promenade and looked at what is there to discover for the coming days. Back in the hotel, a really nice buffet was waiting for us - everyone really gets full here. And the staff is so friendly that you feel more comfortable twice. </p>
        <p> This is how our vacation starts on the sunny island - relaxed, tasty and with a lot of anticipation for the coming days. </p>
